title: Your Keys To A New Beginning! Our 3 Bedroom Is Your New Home!
posting_body: ['Here at Cedar Ridge Apartments, our spacious one, two, and three bedroom apartment homes offer comfortable living rooms, ample kitchen counter-top and cabinet space, and spacious bedrooms.', 'Our personal patios or balconies with stunning grassland views will make you love where you live.', 'Call today to schedule a tour of Cedar Ridge’s apartment homes.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Nearby Soccer Field, Volleyball & Tennis Courts', '- Convenient On-Site Laundry Facilities', '- Ample Off-Street Open Parking', '- Beautiful Grassland Views', '- Gorgeous 1, 2 & 3 Bedroom Apartment Homes', '- Intercom & Telephone Controlled Entry Access System', '- Spacious Bedrooms With Wall Length Closets', '- Master Suite Walk-In Closet (In select homes)', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Cedar Ridge participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Tuesday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Wednesday: 11:00AM-7:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday: 9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Cedar Ridge', '1401 Namekagon Avenue', 'Hudson, WI, 54016', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'JGFIzvx7']
